data.description:
This beautiful 3 bed 2 bath residence is a dream come true for those seeking spacious living and natural beauty.

Step inside to high ceilings in the living room, creating an open and airy atmosphere that invites both relaxation and entertainment. The recently updated kitchen includes all appliances. 

 The property boasts two carports, one of which is generously sized to accommodate an RV

This home sits on one acre of unrestricted land, immerse yourself in the tranquility of nature, with ample room for gardening, recreation, or simply enjoying the serenity that comes with owning your own slice of paradise. Unlock the potential of your dream home with the rare opportunity to purchase an additional 10 acres of adjoining land, seamlessly expanding your property and possibilities. 

Don't miss the opportunity to make this idyllic retreat your own. Embrace the freedom of unrestricted living and seize the chance to create a lifetime of memories in this home!  Call today for your own private showing!
